quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  59,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  59,1,"Allah hi ki tasbeeh ki hai har uss cheez ne jo asmano aur zameen mein hai, aur wohi ghalib aur hakeem hai"
  59,2,"wohi hai jis ne ahal kitaab kafiroon ko pehlay hi hamlay mein unn ke gharon se nikaal bahar kya tumhe hargiz yeh gumaan nah tha ke woh nikal jayen ge, aur woh bhi yeh samjhay baithy thay ke unn ki gurrhyan inhen Allah se bacha len gi magar Allah aisay rukh se unn par aaya jidhar unn ka khayaal bhi nah gaya tha uss ne unn ke dilon mein roab daal diya nateeja yeh howa ke woh khud apne hathon se bhi apne gharon ko barbaad kar rahay thay aur mominoun ke hathon bhi barbaad karwa rahay thay pas Ibrat haasil karo ae deedaa Beena rakhnay walo !"
  59,3,"agar Allah ne unn ke haq mein jala watni nah likh di hoti to duniya hi mein woh inhen azaab day dalta, aur akhirat mein to un ke liye dozakh ka azaab hai hi"
  59,4,"yeh sab kuch is liye howa ke unhon ne Allah aur is ke rasool ka muqaabla kya, aur jo bhi Allah ka muqaabla kere Allah is ko saza dainay mein bohat sakht hai"
  59,5,"tum logon ne khajoron ke jo darakht katay ya jin ko apni jaroon par khara rehne diya, yeh sab Allah hi ke azan se tha aur ( Allah ne yeh azan is liye diya ) taakay fasiqon ko zaleel o khawar kere"
  59,6,"aur jo maal Allah ne unn ke qabzay se nikaal kar apne rasool ki taraf palta diye, woh aisay maal nahi hain jin par tum ne apne ghoray aur oont dorra-ay hon, balkay Allah apne Rasolo-n ko jis par chahta hai tasallut ataa farma deta hai, aur Allah har cheez par Qadir hai"
  59,7,"jo kuch bhi Allah inn bustiyon ke logon se apne rasool ki taraf palta day woh Allah aur rasool aur rishta daaron aur yutaama aur msakin aur musafiron ke liye hai taakay woh tumahray maldaron hi ke darmain gardish nah karta rahay jo kuch Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam tumhen day woh le lau aur jis cheez se woh tum ko rok day is se ruk jao Allah se daro, Allah sakht saza dainay wala hai"
  59,8,( neez woh maal ) unn ghareeb muhajreen ke liye hai jo apne gharon aur jaydadon se nikaal bahar kiye gay hain yeh log Allah ka fazl aur is ki khushnodi chahtay hain aur Allah aur uss ke Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ki himayat par kamar basta rehtay hain yahirasbaaz log hain
  59,9,( aur woh unn logon ke liye bhi hai ) jo inn muhajreen ki aamad se pehlay hi imaan laa kar darul hijrat mein muqeem thay yeh unn logon se mohabbat karte hain jo hijrat kar ke inn ke paas aeye hain aur jo kuch bhi unn ko didya jaye uss ki koi haajat taq yeh apne dilon mein mehsoos nahi karte aur apni zaat par dosaron ko tarjeeh dete hain khuwa apni jagah khud mohtaaj hon haqeeqat yeh hai ke jo log apne dil ki tangi se bacha liye gay wohi Falah panay walay hain
  59,10,"( aur woh unn logon ke liye bhi hai ) jo inn uglo ke baad aeye hain, jo kehte hain ke"" ae hamaray rab, hamein aur hamaray unn sab bhaieyon ko bakhash day jo hum se pehlay imaan laaye hain aur hamaray dilon mein ahal imaan ke liye koi bughz nah rakh, ae hamaray rab, to bara meharban aur Raheem hai """
  59,11,"tum ne dekha nahi unn logon ko jinhon ne munafqat ki rawish ikhtiyar ki hai? yeh apne kafir ahal kitaab bhaieyon se kehte hain"" agar tumhe nikala gaya to hum tumahray sath nikleen ge, aur tumahray maamla mein hum kisi ki baat hargiz nah manen ge, aur agar tum se jung ki gayi to hum tumhari madad karen ge"" magar Allah gawah hai ke yeh log qatee jhutay hain"
  59,12,"agar woh nikalay gay to yeh un ke sath hargiz nah nikleen ge, aur agar unn se jung ki gayi to yeh unn ki hargiz madad nah karen ge, aur agar yeh un ki madad karen bhi to peeth phair jayen ge aur phir kahin se koi madad nah payen ge"
  59,13,"inn ke dilon mein Allah se barh kar tumhara khauf hai, is liye ke yeh aisay log hain jo samajh boojh nahi rakhtay"
  59,14,"yeh kabhi ikathay ho kar ( khulay maidan mein ) tumhara muqaabla nah karen ge, lrhin ge bhi to qilah band bustiyon mein baith kar ya dewaron ke peechay choup kar yeh aapas ki mukhalfat mein barray sakht hain tum aِnhin akhatta samajte ho magar un ke dil aik dosray se phatay hue hain inn ka yeh haal iss liye hai ke yeh be aqal log hain"
  59,15,yeh aُnhi logon ke manind hain jo inn se thori hi muddat pehlay apne kiye ka maza chakh chuke hain aur inn ke liye dard naak azaab hai
  59,16,"inn ki misaal shetan ki si hai ke pehlay woh ensaan se kehta hai ke kufar kar, aur jab ensaan kufar kar baithta hai to woh kehta hai ke mein tujh se buri alzmh hon, mujhe to Allah rab alaalmin se dar lagta hai"
  59,17,"phir dono ka injaam yeh hona hai ke hamesha ke liye jahannum mein jayen, aur zaalmon ki yahi jaza hai"
  59,18,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, Allah se daro, aur har shakhs yeh dekhe ke uss ne kal ke liye kya samaan kya hai Allah se drtay raho, Allah yaqeenan tumahray unn sab aamaal se bakhabar hai jo tum karte ho"
  59,19,"unn logon ki terhan nah ho jao jo Allah ko bhool gay to Allah ne unhen khud apna nafs bhala diya, yahi log fasik hain"
  59,20,dozakh mein jaane walay aur jannat mein jaane walay kabhi yaksaa nahi ho satke jannat mein jaane walay hi asal mein kamyaab hain
  59,21,agar hum ne yeh quran kisi pahar par bhi utaar diya hota to tum dekhte ke woh Allah ke khauf se daba ja raha hai aur phataa parta hai yeh misalein hum logon ke samnay is liye bayan karte hain ke woh ( apni haalat par ) ghhor karen
  59,22,"woh Allah hi hai jis ke siwa koi mabood nahi, gayab aur zahir har cheez ka jan-nay wala, wohi rehman aur Raheem hai"
  59,23,"woh Allah hi hai jis ke siwa koi mabood nahi woh badshah hai nihayat muqaddas, sara sar salamti, aman dainay wala, nigehbaan, sab par ghalib, apna hukum Bazore nafiz karne wala, aur bara hi ho kar rehne wala pak hai Allah uss shirk se jo log kar rahay hain"
  59,24,"woh Allah hi hai jo takhleeq ka mansoobah bananay wala aur is ko nafiz karne wala aur is ke mutabiq soorat giri karne wala hai is ke liye behtareen naam hain har cheez jo asmano aur zameen mein hai uss ki tasbeeh kar rahi hai, aur woh zabardast aur hakeem hai"
